Legs yellowish-brown to brown, without spots. Forelegs light brown, darker than middle and hind ones. All wings hyaline, transparent. Pterostigma almost transparent, opaque with 4–5 cross veins. Hind wings 2.3 times longer than wide, with rounded apex. Costal projection well developed. Three longitudinal veins, cross veins absent. Third vein ends at approximately half of the wing length. Two small intercalaries between second and third veins (
Fig. 2
). Venations of both wings yellowish-brown.
